Linux Tails

- Attacchi DOS -> Tor's Hammer, Slowloris;
- Brute Force Passwords -> OphCrack, Hydra, Aircrack-NG;
- Attacchi mman in the middle -> Ettercap;
- Scansione dei server -> Nmap, Nikito, Vega;

Script example for DoS:
Windows:
:Beginning
ping -n 1 www.example.it
GOTO Beginning

Unix:
while true
do
ping -c1 www.example.com
done
